examples.en: As the illness progressed, his delusions took over and he had violent outbursts.
Work on the ship progressed quickly.
The caravan progressed slowly across the desert.
They progressed to the final round of the tennis tourney.
The Administration's thinking changed as the war progressed.
The screams of the fans grew more frenzied as the concert progressed.
She started with a cleaning job, and progressed to running the company.
There was a large turnout at the commencement of the conference, but the numbers dwindled as it progressed.
